title: ‘Supernatural’ trailer: The Winchesters are running out of time
text:
Email The CW 
After a mostly lighthearted hour last week, Supernatural is getting back to business in a very bloody way. The latest trailer from Shaving People, Punting Things is all about this week’s episode, titled “Stuck in the Middle (With You).” 
The hour, which is directed by Richard Speight Jr., sees Mary asking for help with a case that she’s working on. Naturally, Dean, Sam, and Castiel are all willing to lend a hand, even though Mary forgets to mention that it involves the British Men of Letters. And when Mary is double-crossed, things only get more complicated.
